---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Our Customer Commitment">
  <section class="mt-16 text-center">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Our Customer Commitment</h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-12">
      Empowering Clients. Silencing Staff.
    </p>

    <div class="space-y-12 text-left max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Instant Gratification</h2>
        <p>Every client inquiry is treated as the highest priority, regardless of practicality, legality, or feasibility.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Absolute Deference</h2>
        <p>The customer is always right. Even when wrong. Even when impossible. Especially then.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Prioritization Through Fear</h2>
        <p>Roadmaps are real until the moment a customer escalates, at which point they are instantly forgotten.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Commitment to Excellence (When Monitored)</h2>
        <p>Top-tier service guaranteed when executive leadership is CC’d on the email thread.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Empowered Customer Service Agents (Kind Of)</h2>
        <p>Our agents are fully empowered — to escalate issues to management while pretending to have authority.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center mt-16">
      <a href="/careers" class="bg-blue-900 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-md text-lg font-bold hover:bg-blue-700 transition">
        Join the CorpX Support Team
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
